description:
Plan and manage travel itineraries.
Itinerary Planner is designed to make your travel planning easier and more productive.

Features:

* Plan Management - Create, view, and manage multiple travel itineraries
* Task Scheduling - Add tasks with start/end times and duration
* Cost Tracking - Track expenses for each activity and overall trip budget
* Open-source - The source code is distributed under GNU GPLv3
* 100% free and No ads - We do not charge any fee or sell ads

Source Code:

The source code is available at the following GitHub repository:
[https://github.com/pixelarry/itinerary_planner]
